story.text: We explain how to choose media keys for HTML5 video.  Read [[About Video Plugin]] to understand media keys and the other services supported by the plugin.
Provide a mime video subtype and the URL to the video source.  Example mime video subtypes: [https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Supported_media_formats#File_formats mozilla]
This option can be used to display videos uploaded to wiki with the assets plugin.  [[About Assets Plugin]]
This is an embedded video hosted at Wikipedia. Double-click the caption to see the plugin markup.
